    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) is one gradation below required level due to single-condition testing; this shortfall is accepted given the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs (max E/uval 1.52, max QoI difference 8.3%) and the corroborating evidence from the high-fidelity numerical simulation closure study, which independently confirms QoI predictions within 6.8% of experimental means. The simulation study is assessed as providing complementary and equivalent evidentiary support to an additional experimental campaign. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU.",
